See also [[Smith]]
==English==
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[smiþ]]''
===Noun===
'''smith''' (pl. ''smiths'')

#A [[craftsperson]] who works [[metal]] into desired forms using a [[hammer]] and other tools, sometimes heating the metal to make it more [[workable]].

====Related terms====
*[[smithy]] or [[smiddy]]
*[[smithery]]
*[[blacksmith]]
*[[goldsmith]]
*[[gunsmith]]
*[[silversmith]]
*[[swordsmith]]
*[[tinsmith]]

